decrypt(25.10)                                                  decrypt(25.10)

Name
       decrypt - Decrypts and evaluates a Tcl file that was encrypted with the
       encrypt command

Syntax
       decrypt

       [-help]

       <file_name>

       Decrypts  and  evaluates a Tcl file that was encrypted with the encrypt
       command.

Parameters
       -help  Prints out the command usage.

       <file_name>
              Specifies the name of the Tcl file to be  decrypted  and  evalu-
              ated.

              Data_type: string, required

Related Information
              * encrypt

